OL,3,CCrown court judges to sit at record
OL,4,Clevel to tackle delays ` Justice
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FCrown court judges will sit for a
OL,8,Frecord number of days in the next
OL,9,Ffinancial year as part of Government
OL,10,Fefforts to tackle the backlog of cases.
OL,12,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,13,Fjudges will sit collectively for
OL,14,F110,000 days in the next year, 4,000
OL,15,Fmore than allocated for the previous
OL,16,Fperiod, to help victims see justice
OL,17,Fdone faster.
