OL,3,CCrown court judges to sit at record
OL,4,Clevel to tackle delays ` Justice
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe move comes as the Victims
OL,8,FCommissioner published a report on
OL,9,FTuesday warning that the record levels
OL,10,Fof crown court delays are deepening
OL,11,Fthe trauma of victims and making many
OL,12,Ffeel justice is "out of reach".
OL,14,FMeanwhile a report from the Public
OL,15,FAccounts Committee raised concerns
OL,16,Fministers had "simply accepted" the
OL,17,Frecord-high crown court backlog will
OL,18,Fcontinue to grow and it will wait for
OL,19,Fthe results of the Leveson Review
OL,20,Fbefore planning changes to tackle it.
