OL,3,CCrown court judges to sit at record
OL,4,Clevel to tackle delays ` Justice
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe major review led by Sir Brian
OL,8,FLeveson is expected to report on
OL,9,Freforms to the court system in the
OL,10,Fspring.
OL,12,FIt comes amid a rising backlog in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales which has almost
OL,14,Fdoubled in five years to 73,105 at the
OL,15,Fend of September last year.
OL,17,FMs Mahmood said: "This Government
OL,18,Finherited a record and rising courts
OL,19,Fbacklog, with justice delayed and
OL,20,Fdenied for far too many victims.
