OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,F"Bearing down on that backlog is an
OL,8,Fessential element of our Plan for
OL,9,FChange, bringing offenders to justice
OL,10,Fto keep our streets safe.
OL,12,F"Funding a record number of sitting
OL,13,Fdays is a critical first step.
OL,15,F"But there is more that we must and we
OL,16,Fwill do.
OL,18,F"I have asked Sir Brian Leveson to
OL,19,Fconsider radical reforms to deliver
OL,20,Fthe swifter justice that victims
OL,21,Fdeserve."
