OL,7,FThe extra sitting days will also apply
OL,8,Fto immigration and asylum tribunal
OL,9,Fcases, bringing them to near maximum
OL,10,Fcapacity, to help speed up asylum
OL,11,Fclaims, the Ministry of Justice said.
OL,13,FThe Government confirmed funding for
OL,14,Frepairs and maintenance across the
OL,15,Fcourts and tribunal estate is to rise
OL,16,Ffrom #120 million last year to #148.5
OL,17,Fmillion this year.
