OL,7,FRepairs will include remedial works
OL,8,Ffor crumbling reinforced autoclaved
OL,9,Faerated concrete (Raac) at Harrow
OL,10,FCrown Court, which has been closed
OL,11,Fsince August 2023, and fixing leaking
OL,12,Froofs and out-of-order lifts.
OL,14,FFunding will also be given to new
OL,15,Fcourts being built, such as a 30-
OL,16,Fhearing room tribunal centre at
OL,17,FNewgate Street in London, and a county
OL,18,Fand family court in Reading.
