OL,7,FReacting to the announcement, Law
OL,8,FSociety of England and Wales president
OL,9,FRichard Atkinson said they were
OL,10,Fwelcome steps.
OL,12,FHe added: "But sitting days are still
OL,13,Fnot at the maximum the Lady Chief
OL,14,FJustice has said is possible to
OL,15,Fachieve.
OL,17,F"While the funding increase for court
OL,18,Fmaintenance is only a small fraction
OL,19,Fof the #1.3 billion repairs backlog
OL,20,Ffor courts and tribunals reported by
OL,21,Fthe National Audit Office."
